Part 1039 - Miscellaneous Rules

State Regulations
§ 1039.1 to 1039.2 - Repealed
§ 1039.3 - Notification of right to appeal to defendants appearing pro se

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. § 1039.1 to 1039.2 - Repealed
